rows.label: tev001391_MSG0001
rows.name:
Good day to you, [ST:playername ].
Have you come to check on us?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0002
rows.name:
Rock now has a job, and we are able to live at peace
here in New LA. We owe all of these blessings to you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0003
rows.name:
I do not know how to thank you for all that you
have done.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_JNK0010
rows.name: Deflect

rows.label: tev001391_SEL0011
rows.name: Answer that it's all due to Celica's hard work.

rows.label: tev001391_JNK0020
rows.name: Laud

rows.label: tev001391_SEL0021
rows.name: Credit Rock's courage for this outcome.

rows.label: tev001391_JNK0030
rows.name: Boast

rows.label: tev001391_SEL0031
rows.name:
Say that you also can't comprehend
how truly awesome you are.

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0004
rows.name: Dear me, no. That is most kind, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well, I'm afraid there is precious little that I am
capable of accomplishing by myself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0006
rows.name:
It is thanks to all of you that I am able to function as
a member of this fair city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0007
rows.name:
You are correct! Rock's courage has saved me
time and time again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0008
rows.name: I know that he shall never let me down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0009
rows.name: I am truly fortunate to have him as a friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0010
rows.name: What a delightful sense of humor you have![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0011
rows.name:
That is one of the things I love about this fair cityâ€”
there are so many upbeat and positive people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0012
rows.name:
I think that is part of the reason we were accepted here
so readily.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0013
rows.name:
Until now, we have lived lives of fear and stress,
ever on the run from Samaar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0014
rows.name:
I'd assumed we were doomed to a most miserable
type of existence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0015
rows.name:
It never occurred to me that Rock could make friends
with others and be so...happy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0016
rows.name:
And being able to live in this fair city has done much
to put my own heart at ease.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0017
rows.name: I am so very glad we met back in Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0018
rows.name:
I shall hold these feelings of gratitude close until the day
that I can say that I have repaid my fellow citizens of
New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0019
rows.name: And I know that Rock feels the same.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001391_MSG0020
rows.name:
I do hope you will bear with us while we work to settle
our debt to you.[ST:wait ]
